#### Steps to create a form ####

Step 1: Create a form
Step 2: Add one or many data source
Step 3: Configure the relationship between datasources added in step 2.
Step 4: Add control to the design
Step 5: drag appropriate fields from datasource added in step 2 into the added control from step 4
Step 6: In class declaration of the form, add QueryBuildRange variable
Step 7: Add appropriate sys methods on the datasource depends on business needs
